OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 24 Apr to Sun 3 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure is likely to be centred
OL,7,Fclose to or across the UK through much
OL,8,Fof this period. So many places will be
OL,9,Flargely dry with clear or sunny
OL,10,Fperiods. Colder air will try to push
OL,11,Finto the country from the north toward
OL,12,Fnext weekend, but will probably only
OL,13,Fmake limited progress into the
OL,14,Fnortheast for a brief time, where it
OL,15,Fcould bring a short lived showery
OL,16,Finterlude, some of these wintry. Winds
OL,17,Fwill be mostly light, but briefly
OL,18,Fstronger in the northeast as that
OL,19,Fcolder air tries to come south.
OL,20,FTemperatures will probably be near
OL,21,Fnormal or slightly above for many, but
OL,22,Fwith a risk of colder conditions
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Faffecting the north next weekend.
